                        related" experience. Officers verify this and will refuse
                        applications where claimed experience doesn't match reality.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Including bonuses in wage:</strong> Only your guaranteed
                        base hourly rate counts. Don't include overtime, tips, or
                        annual bonuses.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Wrong NOC code:</strong> Selecting a higher-skill
                        NOC than your actual duties support will lead to refusal.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Expired language test:</strong> Your test must be
                        valid (less than 2 years old) throughout the application process.
                    </li>
                </ul>

